Lv. 1: Stops shooting and plays her guitar 5 times. Every play of her guitar applies 7%(10% with [[Black Cat]]) rate of fire and accuracy debuff on 3 random enemy echelons for 3 seconds. (10s cooldown, 6s initial cooldown.)
Lv. 10: Stops shooting and plays her guitar 5 times. Every play of her guitar applies 12%(15% with [[Black Cat]]) rate of fire and accuracy debuff on 3 random enemy echelons for 3 seconds. (8s cooldown, 6s initial cooldown.)
1010.formBonus:
Affects all guns:
Increases damage by 15%(x1) / 19%(x2) / 23%(x3) / 27%(x4) / 30%(x5)
Increases accuracy by 25%(x1) / 32%(x2) / 38%(x3) / 44%(x4) / 50%(x5)
1010.note: Can equip: night-vision goggles, silencers, hp ammo, microchips, exoskeletons.
